    "title": "trconvert",
    "version": "0.23.43",
    "description": "Reads a grammar from stdin and converts the grammar to/from Antlr version 4\nsyntax. The original grammar must be for a supported type (Antlr2, Antlr3,\nBison, W3C EBNF, Lark). The input and output are Parse Tree Data."
